# Local security workspace (not committed)

Copy this folder to `security/` (gitignored) for internal audit artifacts:

```bash
mkdir -p security/private
cp security/README.example security/README.md  # optional local note
```

## Suggested layout

```
security/
  private/
    OWASP_ASSESSMENT.md    # OWASP mapping + findings (copy from docs/AUDIT*.md)
    AUDIT.md
    AUDIT_GAPS.md
    AUDIT_FIXES.md
    scan-exports/          # Slither, Semgrep SARIF, etc.
```

Move existing reports out of git tracking:

```bash
mv docs/AUDIT.md docs/AUDIT_GAPS.md docs/AUDIT_FIXES.md security/private/ 2>/dev/null || true
```

Regenerate audits locally; never `git add security/` or `docs/AUDIT*.md`.
